				<h3 class="bigger">Ready to dive into the documentation?</h3>
				<p>Crypton is well-documented for beginners looking to understand basic concepts. For more advanced users, Crypton provides features like realtime end-to-end encrypted messaging and custom transactions. Why not take a peek?</p>
				<div>
					<a href="/documentation" class="button orange">See Documentation</a>
